    "body": "### Problem\n\nBasically, I would like the ability to add a prefix or a set number of spaces before the \"--INSERT--\" or ex-command entering prompt and all other similar prompts. there is a cmdheight option but thats not what im looking for. kinda like horizonta padding\n\n### Expected behavior\n\ne.g cmdpadding=1 would put padding of 1 space on the bar. There seems to be literally no way to do this as its hardcoded into neovim and i believe that the more control people have over the software the farther they can go with it. thanks for attending my ted talk and you can just ignore me if this idea seems dumb",
